author: The Current
description:
Soul Asylum plays three songs from 'Slowly But Shirley'
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

Back in November, rock icons Soul Asylum, stopped by The Current studio to perform songs from their 13th studio record, Slowly but Shirley. 

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 High Road
00:03:30 Freak Accident
00:08:00 Black Gold

Musicians
David Pirner – vocals, guitar
Ryan Smith – guitar, backing vocals
